Here is a quick and easy qunioa salad you can make any time of year. It&rsquo;s packed with protein, and what do you know, it&rsquo;s good for you too!&nbsp;
Quinoa Salad Ingredients&nbsp;
1 cup uncooked quinoa 1 1/2 cups water 1 {15-ounce} can black beans, drained and rinsed 1 cup cilantro, finely chopped 1 cup carrots, chopped 1 cup packed spinach leaves, chopped 1/4 cup chives, chopped 1/2 teaspoon kosher salt 1/4 teaspoon fresh ground pepper

